name: Karakuri Komachi mdl 224 "Ninishi"
desc: This card must attack if able. When this face-up card on the field is selected as an attack target, change its battle position. While this card is face-up on the field, once per turn during your Main Phase, you can Normal Summon a "Karakuri" monster in addition to your Normal Summon or Set. (You can only gain this effect once per turn.)
str2: Additional Normal Summon by the effect of "Karakuri Komachi mdl 224 "Ninishi""
